title: 820-4924 no pp5v_so ,s3 , s4 rails
message:
"ppbus_g3h =12v"
Always post exact (2 decimals) voltage for PPBUS_G3H; you'll see later how important is!

Any history available, liquid spillage?
Do you get 3V_3S5/SUS?
If yes, post S5_^WRGD, PM_DSW_PWRGD, PCH_DSWVRMEN, PM_BATLOW_L, PM_RSMRST_L and PM_PWRBTN_L.
Trigger SMC_ONOFF_L (use R5115/16 pads) and check for reaction (drop pulse) at PM_PWRBTN_L.
